          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷心中有事，若是无事，重责一百皮鞭，还不下去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "尤俊达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程咬金",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "豹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尤俊达、程咬金同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二哥，方才过去那是什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟不认识？稳坐雕鞍听愚兄道来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟莫把来人问，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "青面红发似天神。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "班鸠店内程咬金。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要问此人名和姓"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐勣",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "南京收了南京去，北京收了北京游。南北二京全不收，条河两岸度春秋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐勣",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要问此人名和姓"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐勣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥魏徵，二哥李靖，三弟茂公为母许愿，舍药三年，舍了二载，还有一春，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐勣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用药这厢来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来者敢是茂公？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐勣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么说，贤弟冒了风了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐勣",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三片生姜两段葱，一晚温汤用腹中，盖上被子出身汗，哪管你冒风不冒风！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是徐勣？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐勣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么方才冒了风，你又得了食积？下马来，我与你号脉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下马去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐勣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明白了，上马去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有罪了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐勣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是狗皮膏药四张，前心一张，后心一张，左膀一张，右膀一张，这是大红丸，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐勣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一付用在腹中，药往外发，膏药往里发，好似两军阵前，冲锋打仗一般，出"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐勣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一身冷汗，你这病就好了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问用何药引？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐勣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只顾与兄台讲话，把药引都忘记了。虎的心，豹的胆，虎豹二字牢牢紧记，请"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐勣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐勣下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二哥方才过去那是什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟不认识？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不认识。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将马勒后，听愚兄道来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在大街不敢通名姓，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "物吞八卦阴阳能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梨阳县里徐茂公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟你我游来游去，并无比艺，你我回去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "袖儿里常拿三才打"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请二哥观阵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "甚么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请二哥观阵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻听说观阵心纳闷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十分精神少九分。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想起了高堂老娘亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哭一声老娘心难忍，我的娘吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何人送进秦家坟？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他说我秦家是绝门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那边来了卖马人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（罗成上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗成",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卖马吓卖马！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来者敢是罗成？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗成",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一匹马未从讲价，就说成与不成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为兄是秦琼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗成",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你穷算你命苦，哪个周济你不成？我这马如同虎豹一般，虎豹二字，牢牢紧记，"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗成",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（罗成下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一言未尽罗成到，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒叫豪杰喜眉梢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八弟花枪命难逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再叫贤弟听根苗！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟此为何阵？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨龄贼呀时衰了"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喜盈盈来催黄骠"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金锁八卦连环斗底大阵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪门进？哪门出？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "生门进，休门出。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为兄杀在昏迷之间，哪晓得生门、休门？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为弟枪头之上，挂着三尺红罗，随罗而进随罗而出。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愚兄马上多谢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "观此阵我把雄心退，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用枪一指骂老贼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "摆下八卦九重雷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中营安下振天雷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "设谋定计拿老贼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "细思想朋友还要为。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再叫贤弟听明白！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟此为何桥？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杏马旗插在青龙背"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "营门外大炮摆几对"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众家兄弟阵前对"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "低下头来想半悔"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "佐黄骠闯在紫金对"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "绝命桥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何为绝命桥？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨龄与二哥交战，胜过二哥则罢了，胜不过二哥，将桥梁拆断，把二哥活活淹"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "死在内。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你二哥一死倒也罢了，岂不害了看桥之人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨龄贼吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "观此阵把我的胆唬破，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上是桥来下是河。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苦了看桥小哥哥！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟此为何炮？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你二哥一死还罢了"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "振中胆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何为振中胆？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨龄与二哥交战，胜不过二哥，将此炮点着，把二哥活活振死在内。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你二哥一死还在罢了，岂不苦了看炮之人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗周",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只要二哥一死，哪管看炮之人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨龄贼吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "勒马我把贤弟叫，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫声贤弟听根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来世与你把香烧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦琼、罗周同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "秦琼→程咬金",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "程咬金→罗周",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "罗周→尤俊达",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "尤俊达→罗周",
          "turns": 2
